title: RetroShare06-Help-Documents-User-Guides
description:
Retroshare 0.6 Help Documents, Setup-Guides, Steps and Static Webpages all designed to help new users setup Regular Retroshare networks and as well as Retroshare via Tor networks and quickly connect with global Retroshare users.
.
Contains the RS06-Docs folder in 4 different compression algorithms to address all Windows, Mac and Linux users. Each compressed file is exactly the same after decompressing. Each compressed file has a sha256sum file listed in a text file.
.
Contains the following files
RS06-Docs.7z
RS06-Docs.tar
RS06-Docs.tar.gz
RS06-Docs.zip
RS06-Docs.sha256sum.txt
